nodes.text: A member of the Mandalorian Clan Kryze pledged his Mandalorian clan to Lady Bo-Katan Kryze and the Mandalorian resistance against the Galactic Empire along with several other Mandalorian factions following the Mission to Mandalore during the Mandalorian Civil War. The member's support, along with the other Mandalorians, allowed Lady Bo-Katan to become Mand'alor
